Purpose scope of use: Provide message push service, collect and collect device identifiers
(IMEI/Mac/android ID/IDFA/OPENUDID/GUID, SIM card IMSI information)
, which are used to uniquely identify the device, so as to push messages to the target device. Collect geographical location to identify push channels and improve the regional coverage of message push.
(5) com.umeng.umsdk:amp:1.7.0
Purpose scope of use: collect device identifiers
(IMEI/Mac/android ID/IDFA/OPENUDID/GUID, SIM card IMSI information)
, which are used to uniquely identify devices, so as to provide device application performance monitoring services; provide anti-cheating by collecting location information service, eliminate cheating devices, and troubleshoot the cause of application performance crashes.
(6) cn.jiguang.sdk:jpush:5.0.0
Purpose scope of use: Provide message push service, collect and collect device identifiers
(IMEI/Mac/android ID/IDFA/OPENUDID/GUID, SIM card IMSI information)
, which are used to uniquely identify the device, so as to push messages to the target device. Collect geographical location to identify push channels and improve the regional coverage of message push.
(7) org.litepal.guolindev:core:3.2.3
The database completes the operations of creating tables, adding, deleting, and querying push message information
